<<<<<System requirements>>>>> Before running this container, ensure your system meets the following requirements.

        Apptainer / Singularity runtime
        Linux x86_64 architecture

        NVIDIA GPU with CUDA support (required for RAPIDS libraries; JupyterLab
        and shell access work without a GPU)
        NVIDIA Container Toolkit for GPU access
        CUDA-compatible GPU driver

        Minimum 8GB RAM (16GB+ recommended for larger datasets)
        Minimum 10GB free disk space for container and cache

        For multi-node clusters: InfiniBand fabric recommended for best
        performance (UCX transport); Ethernet also supported (TCP transport)

<<<<</System requirements>>>>>
